ygData.messageBody:
Hi Ryan greetings from a fellow TNian...<br>Hmmm
at 14 you should still be getting birthday money
from the grands..start offering to clean up stuff for
cash and announce you are saving for a computer.
(Adults like that kinda stuff) LOL as a Mom of a 9 year
old...if she told me she was saving for something I would
help as much as I could (something about teaching
resposibility hehehe). Good luck and Happy
Hunting!<br><br>Yodwynn(Quixotic Union of Optimists)<br>High-Elven Cleric of
Povar<br>9th Season
